title: Final Fantasy XI Ultimate Collection w/Free to play instruction
description:
Final Fantasy XI complete installer

Also includes instructions on how to play on for Free.
   
http://nasomi.com/ - Forums and installation instructions  
http://nasomi.net/ - Live chat & Help
 
The largest and most table private FFXI server.
Nasomi has over 1200 players and growing steadily.

Great opportunity to go back and camp the NM's
you never got a chance to before, finish the
story lines that you always wanted to see the
ending to! Play with other players who truly
love the game. There's many free MMORPGs but only
one that is great. Dedicated players, friendly
staff, stable server hardware, this is the game
that you've been waiting for
